SQL Project

University Project - SQL Database Management: Exams

This database offers a summary of exam schedules and details for each exam. It contains detailed information about professors (title, first name, last name, department), courses (name, code, category, ECTS credits, year offered), student registration information for exams (student ID, first name, last name, year of study), and exams themselves (exam date, time, and location).

Developed additional Views for customer reports:

Created an SQL query using JOIN operations to merge multiple many-to-many tables in the Quanpedia SQLite database, consolidating customer data and extracting 450 samples into a single SQL view for reporting purposes.

Excel Dashboard: Google Analytics Website Performance Analysis (2014)

Data Science
Python Data Science Project - Time Series

Time Series: Analysis of Alcohol Beverage Sales during COVID-19:

This project examines time series data of monthly wholesale alcohol beverage sales from 1992 until now. The analysis highlights a notable surge in sales during the COVID-19 confinement period, illustrating a significant shift in consumer behavior compared to previous years.
